dictionary.description: Fei Yan, eldest daughter of the Fei family, graduated from the Academy with both a promising career and the adulation of her fellow students. But the celebrations were cut tragically short as old grudges birthed a new conflict across the land. She barely had any time to rest before the government swept her up to lead its campaign against uncontrolled use of magical beasts. As the tensions threatened to spill over into open warfare, Yan found herself with her friends as they tracked down the heart of the matter: a magical vortex that led to a new land. It took several well-placed punches and more than the usual gout of flame from her dragon, but at last they had secured the rift. However, the masterminds of the rebellion had escaped, a matter than Yan knew she would rue for days to come...
dictionary.evolution: I've become stronger. Is power justice?
dictionary.fusion: I can feel myself getting stronger. Yuan, how are you still so tiny but so round and full? Get bigger, why don't you?
dictionary.summon: Even though you summoned me, that does not mean you get to order me around!
